      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个顺序。提交A需要有个明确的ID标识，方便在cherry-pick的时候引用。标题可以写成\"Cherry-pick from main (top-to-bottom)\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit id",
        "A",
        "title"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先搭建框架：设置标题，然后用gitGraph TB定义从上到下的布局，开头放一个commit，接着branch develop创建分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
